{
  "stem": "6195.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't-- at which point was I?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when there was the [NON-ENGLISH], action, what-- which means that they wanted to lower the number of living Jews, to put it mildly-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they would come in one morning with-- in their cars, in-- on horses, and-- mounted on horses.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there were so many of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And suddenly we have to go to the [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Arbeitsamt, ?] which is the employment office.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there, they will give us new [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] papers to enable us to stay in the ghetto, or simply go-- be taken, in other way-- in other words.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one morning, we got up, and there it is.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Thousands of peoples in front of that employment office.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was with my sister.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But at that time, my brother slept-- he worked in a hospital, and so he slept in this hospital, because the room was so little that if the three of us were together in the room, my sister and I slept in the bed, and my brother had to sleep in the-- in a sort of like a-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in a chair, we-- rocking chair, sort of.",
      "word_count": 70
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It wasn't a rocking chair.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyhow, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] so, because he slept in the hospital, I said to my sister, let's go and get the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Thousands upon thousands of people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But then again, you knew that one and that one who kept order, and Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Not Germans.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish police, but they were-- I knew them from before the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Two of them were pretty Orthodox, too.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
